The global ambulatory healthcare information technology (IT) market is segmented based on the product and service, application, deployment, and end-user. In terms of product and service, the market includes healthcare provider solutions, healthcare IT outsourcing services, and healthcare payer solutions. The application segment consists of practice management software, patient management software, integrated solutions, e-prescribing solutions, and population health management. When considering deployment, the market is categorized into on-premise and cloud-based solutions. Lastly, the end-users of ambulatory healthcare IT encompass hospitals, clinics, and other healthcare facilities.

